text: Carl Beck-Friis (5 December 1921 - 12 March 2005) was a Swedish sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Swedish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sweden Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
